'''千禧高峰會'''（{{lang-en|Millennium Summit}}）是於2000年9月6日<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.undemocracy.com/generalassembly_55/meeting_3 |title=General Assembly Session 55, Meeting 3 |work=undemocracy.com |date=2000-09-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070710155019/http://www.undemocracy.com/generalassembly_55/meeting_3 |archivedate=2007-07-10 |accessdate=2011-07-12 }}</ref>至9月8日<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.undemocracy.com/generalassembly_55/meeting_8 |title=General Assembly Session 55, Meeting 8 |work=undemocracy.com |date=2000-09-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070926234255/http://www.undemocracy.com/generalassembly_55/meeting_8 |archivedate=2007-09-26 |accessdate=2011-07-12 }}</ref>在[[紐約市|紐約市]][[聯合國總部大樓|聯合國總部大樓]]舉行，由世界各國領袖參與、為期三天的會議，旨在討論21世紀以後[[聯合國|聯合國]]的地位和角色<ref name="BBCagenda">{{cite news |first= |last= |authorlink= |author= |coauthors= |title=UN summit agenda; The largest gathering of world leaders in history meets in New York to discuss the role of the United Nations in the 21st century. |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/904903.stm |work= |publisher=[[BBC|BBC News]] |date=2000-12-07 |accessdate=2006-11-22 |archive-date=2020-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200916113114/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/904903.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在會議後，世界各國領袖正式批准[[千禧年宣言|千禧年宣言]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.globalpolicy.org/msummit/millenni/index.htm |title=The Millennium Summit and Its Follow Up |accessdate=2006-11-22 |author= |authorlink= |coauthors= |date= |year= |month= |work= |publisher=Global Policy Forum |pages= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090503145139/http://www.globalpolicy.org/msummit/millenni/index.htm |archivedate=2009-05-03 |quote= |dead-url=no }}</ref>。千禧高峰會是截至2000年為止，史上規模最龐大的世界各國領袖會議<ref name="BBCagenda" />。千禧高峰會在五年後由[[2005年世界高峰會|世界高峰會]]接續，於2005年9月14日至9月16日舉行。

